---
<Layout>
  <h1>MENU</h1>
  <section>
  <div class="drink_container">
    <div class="menu_drink_box">
    <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Logo">
  <h1>To Drink</h1>
 
  {data.map ((menu) => {
    if (menu.menu_category == "Drink") {
      return (
        <article class="menu_item">
            <p>{menu.slug} - {menu.price}</p>
        </article>
    );
  } 
})}

  {data.map ((menu) => {
    if (menu.menu_category == "Drink_2") {
      return (
        <article class="menu_item">
            <p>{menu.slug} - {menu.price}</p>
        </article>
    );
  }
})}
</div>

    <div class="menu_new_box">
    <h2>New</h2>
    <p>Try our "Foam Of The Season" for your matcha or latte</p>
    <p>3,-</p>
  {data.map ((menu) => {
  if (menu.new) {
    return (
        <div class="menu_item">
            <p>{menu.slug}</p>
        </div>
    );
  }
  })}
  <p class="footer_note">Ask the baristas about any allergies</p>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="menu_food_box">
  <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Logo">
 <h1>To Eat</h1>
 
  {data.map ((menu) => {
  if (menu.menu_category == "Food") {
    return (
        <article class="menu_item">
            <p>{menu.slug} - {menu.price}</p>
        </article>
    );
  }
  })}
  <p class="footer_note">Ask the baristas about any allergies</p>
</div>
</section>



<div class="frametext_1">
<h2>BEHIND THE SCENES</h2>
<p>At Fred's, our menu is carefully curated based on what we enjoy the most when visiting a coffee bar.</p>
<p>We believe that good coffee is all about personality, so we've added our own creative twists to classic drinks</p> <p>- from signature matchas to flavorful lattes.</p>

<p>Whether you're in the mood for something sweet like a fresh pastry, or something savory to keep you going,</p> <p>we've got a little bit of everything.</p>
<p>It's all made with love - and with a focus on flavor, quality, and a cozy vibe you won't find anywhere else.</p>
</div>


<div class="collab_emely">
  <div class="flex">
<div>
<img src={matchaIllustration.src} alt="Matcha_illustration" />
</div>
    
<div class="frametext_2">
<h3>Available on June 1st!</h3>
<p>In collaboration with Emely Moraitis, we've created a Pistachio Matcha - a fun and fresh new way to enjoy your matcha.</p>
<p>This unique blend brings together the earthy depth of matcha with the smooth, nutty flavor of pistachio - a combination we're pretty excited about!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="frametext_3">
<h2>ABOUT OUR MENU</h2>
